staging: rtl8723bs: use WLAN_EID_HT_CAPABILITY

Replace unique WLAN_EID_HT_CAP, _HT_CAPABILITY_IE_, and EID_HTCapability
with kernel provided WLAN_EID_HT_CAPABILITY from linux/ieee80211.h.

